3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Do not forget to specify WHERE clause in DELETE or UPDATE statement or it will modify your entire table.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
By default, MySQL Workbench runs in a safe update mode preventing users to make accidental updates.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:59:00,000
